你能够调用以下的API:
{'name': 'NewsAPI.get_articles', 'description': 'This function retrieves articles based on a query, country, and category.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'query', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The search query.'}, {'name': 'country', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The country code.'}, {'name': 'category', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The category of news.'}, {'name': 'number_of_articles', 'type': 'INTEGER', 'description': 'The number of articles to retrieve.'}], 'return_data': [{'name': 'articles', 'description': 'A list of articles, each containing the title, source, and publication date.'}]}
请直接生成JSON格式的回复. 不要在回复中增加注释(//).

{
    // 你这一步的目标
    "目标": string;
    // 你要调用的API名称
    "名称": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "参数输入": Record<string, any>;
}
